    "Since the underlying RS is content based, the recommendation is made based on the similarity between the target article and the journal profiles.",
    "However, explanation EE3, which consists of the list of similar articles published in the recommended journal, could be considered as a type of item style explanation.",
    "Our proposal is distinctly local, as it provides an individualized explanation for each recommended item.",
    "Additionally, it is non-personalized, given that, despite adapting results to the target paper, we do not consider any information (such as interests or preferences) pertaining to the individual seeking the recommendation.",
    "The only information supplied by the user is the title and abstract of the target article."
